'''Hfredium''' was a [[Mineral/Legends|mineral]] used in the construction of [[Starship/Legends|starships]]. It was combined with [[chanlon]] to make a deep [[Color/Legends|red]] alloy known as [[Havod/Legends|havod]]. It was [[Mining/Legends|mined]] on [[Brosi]], [[Nkllon/Legends|Nkllon]], [[Ongary IX]], and [[Shiffrin]], among other [[Planet/Legends|planets]], as well as the [[Tava Yagen]] and [[Pembric asteroid field|Pembric]] [[Asteroid/Legends|asteroid]] [[Asteroid field|fields]]. The price of Hfredium during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] averaged 110 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] per [[Kilogram/Legends|kilogram]]. Hfredium was among the minerals captured from [[Nomad City]] in [[Mitth'raw'nuruodo/Legends|Thrawn's]] raid on Nkllon.

